    "Management": {
      "text": "Scalp laceration can be repaired with staples or if the patient has enough hair with\nHair Apposition Technique\nby twisting hair together and using dermabond.\nCan bleed a lot, consider figure of 8 stitch to help with hemostasis\nOften accompanied by hematomas which may require evacuation for proper skin alignment",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
